(13908, 1, '2020-08-05 05:17:31', '2020-08-05 05:17:31', '[vc_row][vc_column][themestek-custom-heading text=\"Canada Education\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left\"][vc_column_text]Canada is fast emerging as the popular choice for higher studies as the destination for offers a plethora of opportunities for international students who plan to pursue their higher education in the country. Canada is home to some of the top 100 universities in the world. Students whostudy in Canada<strong></strong>can enjoy not just top notch academics, expert faculty and the best research facilities but also a significantly greater employ-ability, after graduation. Canadian courses are of 1 to 3 years and after earning your degree / diploma, you are entitled to get minimum one year of work visa, during which you can apply for PR. With low crime rate, Canada is one of the safest countries in the world.[/vc_column_text][themestek-custom-heading text=\"Why Study In Canada?\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left\"][vc_column_text]The number of international students studying in Canada is over 300,000, a figure that is constantly growing. Many of these students are choosing Canada over other developed countries because of certain advantages that studying in Canada can bring. Individuals who study in Canada receive top-quality and internationally-respected education, preparing them for professional pursuits in Canada or abroad. Yet, the cost of tuition and living fees in Canada are generally lower than in other developed countries.\n\nInternational students in Canada are in an excellent position to develop their career in Canada and stay permanently. The decision you have already made tostudy in Canada places you in a unique position.As an international student, you can take full advantage of the opportunities offered by Canada.\n<ul class=\"ourservices\">\n 	<li>Work while studying</li>\n 	<li>Bring family members to join you in Canada</li>\n 	<li>Obtain a Post-Graduation Work Permit upon graduation</li>\n 	<li>Gain invaluable Canadian work experience</li>\n 	<li>Discover your pathway to permanent residence</li>\n 	<li>Secure permanent resident status, and ultimately Canadian citizenship</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][themestek-custom-heading text=\"Work while studying\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left\"][vc_column_text]A Canadian study permit doesnt just grant you the right to attend university or college, it also grants the student, the right to work off-campus for up to 20 hours per week during regular academic sessions, and full-time during scheduled academic breaks.This opportunity is generally not afforded to students who decided to study in other countries, such as the United States. It allows the student to make some money to fund his/her ongoing studies and living costs, all the while giving the student connections in the local labor market. These professional networks could be the lead into landing a great job upon graduation. Under the Post-Graduation Work Permit, a student can obtain a work permit valid for up to three years, depending on the duration of his/her study program.\n<ul class=\"ourservices\">\n 	<li>No job offers required.</li>\n 	<li>Work with any employer across Canada and change job when you want to.</li>\n 	<li>Get that all-important Canadian work experience as you work towards obtaining permanent residence.</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][themestek-custom-heading text=\"The Admission Process\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left\"][vc_column_text]Once you decided your University or College, we will process your applications and get back to you with an answer in the shortest possible time duration. We will ask you for all the relevant documents and support you for taking the IELTS English language test, helping you select dates of test and any tutorials that you would require. If all your relevant documents are in order and your IELTS score is at the acceptable level, we will help you with the complete online application process. Once you are accepted by the university/college, we will help you in processing all other relevant Government documents that you would need for your study permit.\nWe have also tied up with many banking institutions to help with your University fees forStudy in Canada. The Bank you chose will ease your loan processing and get it disbursed in the shortest possible time frame. We always provide you with choices for top colleges &amp; bestuniversities in Canada.\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner gap=\"0px\" disable_element=\"yes\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"13721\" img_size=\"530*300\" el_class=\"ts-border-radius-1\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][themestek-list icon_type=\"themestek_liviza_business_icon\" icon_icon_themestek_liviza_business_icon=\"themestek-liviza-business-icon themestek-liviza-business-icon-check\" line1=\"R28lMjB0byUyMHRoZSUyMG9mZmljaWFsJTIwd2Vic2l0ZSUyMElFTFRTJTIwYW5kJTIwY3JlYXRlJTIwcHJvZmlsZS4=\" line2=\"Q2hlY2slMjBJbmZvcm1hdGlvbiUyMHByb3ZpZGUlMjBpbiUyMHlvdXIlMjBwYXNzcG9ydC4=\" line3=\"U3BlYWtpbmclMjBvciUyMHdyaXRpbmclMjBzY29yZSUyMHJldmlldyUyMGZvcm0lMjB5b3VyJTIwZXhhbS4=\" line4=\"QWRkaXRpb25hbCUyMHJlcG9ydHMlMjBpbnN0aXR1dGlvbiUyMG9mJTIwY29hY2hpbmclMjBjZW50ZXI=\" line5=\"TmVlZCUyMGV4cGVydGlzZSUyMGhlbHAlMkMlMjB3aGVyZXZlciUyMHlvdSUyMGluJTIwdGhlJTIwd29ybGQu\" css=\".vc_custom_1580792535630{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}\" el_class=\"themestek-list-sep\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row disable_element=\"yes\"][vc_column][themestek-custom-heading text=\"How to Prepare for IELTS Exam\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left\"][vc_single_image image=\"13754\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"ts-border-radius-1\" css=\".vc_custom_1582005531976{padding-top: 10px !important;}\"][vc_row_inner gap=\"0px\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Listening\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:left\" google_fonts=